  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\"><img alt=\"House Hoare 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/50px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/75px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/100px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Qhorwyn Hoare<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Cunning</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\"><img alt=\"House Hoare 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/50px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/75px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f7/House_Hoare_2.svg/100px-House_Hoare_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Qhorwyn_Hoare.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Qhorwyn Hoare.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/29/Qhorwyn_Hoare.png/350px-Qhorwyn_Hoare.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"313\" srcset=\"/images/2/29/Qhorwyn_Hoare.png 1.5x\" /></a><div>Qhorwyn's death, as depicted in <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>: <i>Histories &amp; Lore</i>.</div></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nQhorwyn Hoare</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"King of the Iron Islands\">King of the Iron Islands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Successor</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Harwyn_Hoare\" title=\"Harwyn Hoare\">Harwyn Hoare</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nQhorwyn the Cunning</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\">House Hoare</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\nEldest son<br /><a href=\"/index.php/Harlan_Hoare\" title=\"Harlan Hoare\">Harlan Hoare</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Harwyn_Hoare\" title=\"Harwyn Hoare\">Harwyn Hoare</a><br />Grandmother of <a href=\"/index.php/Qhorin_Volmark\" title=\"Qhorin Volmark\">Qhorin Volmark</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Qhorwyn Hoare</b>, known as <b>Qhorwyn the Cunning</b>, was a <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"King of the Iron Islands\">King of the Iron Islands</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\">House Hoare</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Behind_the_Scenes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Behind the Scenes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Qhorwyn_Hoare&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Qhorwyn was shrewd and avaricious.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Qhorwyn_Hoare&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Qhorwyn was a shrewd <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"King of the Iron Islands\">King of the Iron Islands</a> who avoided war and instead gathered wealth during his reign. He tripled the size of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\">House Hoare</a>'s fleets and ordered the creation of additional <a href=\"/index.php/Armament\" title=\"Armament\">armament</a> to dissuade enemies from attacking.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Qhorwyn's eldest son died of <a href=\"/index.php/Greyscale\" title=\"Greyscale\">greyscale</a>. When his third son, <a href=\"/index.php/Harwyn_Hoare\" title=\"Harwyn Hoare\">Harwyn</a>, returned to the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a> from adventuring two years later, Qhorwyn was dying. The king's middle son, Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Harlan_Hoare\" title=\"Harlan Hoare\">Harlan Hoare</a>, died after falling from a horse while Qhorwyn was lying ill. Though it was said to be an accident, Harlan's death was considered suspicious by some, especially when King Qhorwyn passed six days later.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Harwyn succeeded Qhorwyn as king, and the Hardhand soon used his father's strengthened military to conquer the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> and become the first <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Isles_and_the_Rivers\" title=\"King of the Isles and the Rivers\">King of the Isles and the Rivers</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Qhorwyn_Hoare&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>War is bad for trade. Weakness invites attack. To have peace, we must be strong.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Qhorwyn to the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Qhorwyn_Hoare&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span><